Hero

We have developed the hero component for admint.io, which matches the design currently displayed on the live site.

How to use?

To use the hero component you need to import lib.ftd inside your .ftd file, as shown below:
null
-- import: public-pages/lib

-- import: public-pages/lib
Once you import the lib inside your .ftd file, use the hero component by adding all required attributes of it.
Input
null
-- lib.hero: Deliver refreshing Web 3.0 campaigns!
cta-text: Get Started
cta-link: https://admint.io/

Build your brand's fan-base in web 3.0 with us!

-- lib.hero: Deliver refreshing Web 3.0 campaigns!
cta-text: Get Started
cta-link: https://admint.io/

Build your brand's fan-base in web 3.0 with us!
Output

Deliver refreshing Web 3.0 campaigns!

Deliver refreshing Web 3.0 campaigns!

Build your brand’s fan-base in web 3.0 with us!
Get Started
